{"tid":585804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩釣魚機輸唔起　男子深宵折返機舖打劫「復仇」","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T04:16:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba835476560a7dac570165eeac9636fc57ece618","tid":585804,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時許，一名男子突然闖入葵涌屏富徑13號地下一間遊戲機舖，行劫收銀處一名68歲姓施男職員，搶走約3,000元後逃去無蹤，職員報警求助，警員到場四下搜索，暫未見賊蹤。據悉，涉案男子為本地人，有人認得疑人較早時在上址機舖流連，分多次時段在機舖內打釣魚機，惟多次均玩輸。不排除有人深深不忿，趁機舖於深宵臨打烊，最少人的時段前來「復仇」。據知上址機舖屬於「正經」型，並非違法的賭博釣魚機舖。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列作「搶劫」，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。正追緝一名年約25歲至35歲男子，身高約1.7米，案發時身穿灰色外套、深色長褲、白色運動鞋，戴眼鏡、口罩及藍色鴨舌帽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/166429/thumbnail/8a470c5755c8417446b5734973a372e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F166429%2Fthumbnail%2F8a470c5755c8417446b5734973a372e8.jpg&h=eb62e88e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b626692f5af4de47b482b414259b03ee13a01b86","tid":585804,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係人都知機鋪果d入兩三蚊抽幾千蚊果d都係唔會中"},{"pid":"f248efdfb4efb24b288dbb0829a51a527e5f3c4f","tid":585804,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"其實點解咁多廢中玩部釣魚機"},{"pid":"6a70ded8ba223091f3290ebeb614e8910e325997","tid":585804,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5162c6ca1c26742e6008cffbdb347d3f9658ee","tid":585804,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"正經」型"},{"pid":"1bba81b7fa575b28c29575cbbe8a31a2baf65596","tid":585804,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f248efdfb4efb24b288dbb0829a51a527e5f3c4f","tid":585804,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"其實點解咁多廢中玩部釣魚機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"好似話啲分可以換返錢"}]}